PROJECT NAME

MyPA (My Personal Accounts)

Tagline: Simply Assist

Overview

MyPA is a cloud-based credit management platform that acts as an intermediary between businesses (shops, service providers) and their customers.

The platform maintains secure ledgers of customer credit purchases, payments, outstanding balances, and account history.

Customers can log in to view their own credit accounts while businesses can manage customers, products, invoices, collections, and reports.

The system follows a strict RBAC model with separate dashboards for:

Super Admin
Business Owner
Staff
Customer

The entire solution consists of two completely separate projects.

